---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Weekly Briefing"
  description="Weekly summary of consequential AI developments, benchmark movement, provider changes, and disputed claims."
>
  <div class="wrap" style="max-width:42rem;">
    <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb" class="meta" style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
      <a href="/briefing/daily">Briefings</a> &rsaquo; Weekly
    </nav>

    <h1>Weekly Briefing</h1>
    <p class="meta" style="margin-top:0.25rem;">Week ending 12 July 2026</p>

    <p style="margin-top:1.5rem;padding:0.75rem;background:var(--surface-2);border-radius:var(--radius);font-size:0.9rem;">
      <strong>Phase 1 placeholder.</strong> Automated weekly briefings with benchmark movement and provider comparison changes begin in Phase 3.
    </p>

    <section style="margin-top:2rem;">
      <h2>Most consequential developments</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.25rem;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.5rem;">
        <li>New frontier model launch — independent benchmarks pending</li>
        <li>Provider API pricing dropped 40% industry-wide on mid-tier models</li>
        <li>Major prompt injection vulnerability patched across agent frameworks</li>
        <li>EU AI Act enforcement guidance published</li>
        <li>Open-weight model surpasses proprietary models on 16 GB consumer hardware</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-top:2rem;">
      <h2>Most disputed claims this week</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.25rem;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.5rem;">
        <li>Vendor coding benchmark claims — no independent verification yet available</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-top:2rem;">
      <h2>What changed since last week</h2>
      <p class="meta">
        A new frontier model released. API prices dropped across providers. Agent framework security patches issued. Regulatory guidance published for EU deployments.
      </p>
    </section>

    <div style="margin-top:2rem;">
      <a href="/rss/daily.xml" style="border:1px solid var(--accent);color:var(--accent);padding:0.5rem 1rem;border-radius:var(--radius);font-size:0.9rem;text-decoration:none;">Subscribe via RSS</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
